I"Ò<ol>
  <li>Create empty folder:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">mkdir </span>empty
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Delete files and folders recursively:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>rsync <span class="nt">-a</span> <span class="nt">--delete</span> empty/ &lt;<span class="nv">$FOLDER_TO_DELETE</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
<span class="nb">rm</span> <span class="nt">-rf</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$FOLDER_TO_DELETE</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> empty
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

